PROBLEM
------------------------------
You are visiting San Francisco for the day and want to meet as many friends as possible. Solve the problem by considering various different schedules and picking the best one to optimize your goals.

Travel distances (in minutes):
Marina District to Mission District: 20.
Mission District to Marina District: 19.

CONSTRAINTS: You arrive at Marina District at 9:00AM. Stephanie will be at Mission District from 10:30AM to 1:30PM. You'd like to meet Stephanie for a minimum of 120 minutes.

Your response should start with 'SOLUTION:'.
================================================================================


ENVIRONMENT
------------------------------
You are visiting San Francisco for the day and want to meet as many friends as possible. Solve the problem by considering various different schedules and picking the best one to optimize your goals.

Travel distances (in minutes):
Marina District to Mission District: 20.
Mission District to Marina District: 19.

CONSTRAINTS: You arrive at Marina District at 9:00AM. Stephanie will be at Mission District from 10:30AM to 1:30PM. You'd like to meet Stephanie for a minimum of 120 minutes.

Your response should start with 'SOLUTION:'.
================================================================================


FINAL-PLAN
------------------------------
<domain>
(define (domain meet-stephanie)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :negative-preconditions :fluents)
  (:types
    location
    agent
  )
  (:constants
    marina mission - location
    visitor - agent
  )
  (:predicates
    (at ?l - location)
  )
  (:functions
    (now) - number
    (met-stephanie) - number
    (open-stephanie) - number
    (close-stephanie) - number
    (tt ?from - location ?to - location) - number
  )

  (:action wait-1
    :parameters ()
    :precondition (and)
    :effect (increase (now) 1)
  )

  (:action travel
    :parameters (?from - location ?to - location)
    :precondition (at ?from)
    :effect (and
      (not (at ?from))
      (at ?to)
      (increase (now) (tt ?from ?to))
    )
  )

  (:action meet-1
    :parameters ()
    :precondition (and
      (at mission)
      (>= (now) (open-stephanie))
      (< (now) (close-stephanie))
    )
    :effect (and
      (increase (now) 1)
      (increase (met-stephanie) 1)
    )
  )
)
</domain>
<problem>
(define (problem meet-stephanie-prob)
  (:domain meet-stephanie)
  (:init
    (at marina)
    (= (now) 0)
    (= (met-stephanie) 0)
    (= (open-stephanie) 90)
    (= (close-stephanie) 270)
    (= (tt marina mission) 20)
    (= (tt mission marina) 19)
  )
  (:goal
    (and
      (>= (met-stephanie) 120)
    )
  )
)
</problem>
================================================================================


DOMAIN
------------------------------
(define (domain meet-stephanie)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :negative-preconditions :fluents)
  (:types
    location
    agent
  )
  (:constants
    marina mission - location
    visitor - agent
  )
  (:predicates
    (at ?l - location)
  )
  (:functions
    (now) - number
    (met-stephanie) - number
    (open-stephanie) - number
    (close-stephanie) - number
    (tt ?from - location ?to - location) - number
  )

  (:action wait-1
    :parameters ()
    :precondition (and)
    :effect (increase (now) 1)
  )

  (:action travel
    :parameters (?from - location ?to - location)
    :precondition (at ?from)
    :effect (and
      (not (at ?from))
      (at ?to)
      (increase (now) (tt ?from ?to))
    )
  )

  (:action meet-1
    :parameters ()
    :precondition (and
      (at mission)
      (>= (now) (open-stephanie))
      (< (now) (close-stephanie))
    )
    :effect (and
      (increase (now) 1)
      (increase (met-stephanie) 1)
    )
  )
)
================================================================================


PROBLEM
------------------------------
(define (problem meet-stephanie-prob)
  (:domain meet-stephanie)
  (:init
    (at marina)
    (= (now) 0)
    (= (met-stephanie) 0)
    (= (open-stephanie) 90)
    (= (close-stephanie) 270)
    (= (tt marina mission) 20)
    (= (tt mission marina) 19)
  )
  (:goal
    (and
      (>= (met-stephanie) 120)
    )
  )
)
================================================================================

------------------------------
You are visiting San Francisco for the day and want to meet as many friends as possible. Solve the problem by considering various different schedules and picking the best one to optimize your goals.

Travel distances (in minutes):
Richmond District to Financial District: 22.
Financial District to Richmond District: 21.

CONSTRAINTS: You arrive at Richmond District at 9:00AM. Betty will be at Financial District from 5:15PM to 9:45PM. You'd like to meet Betty for a minimum of 60 minutes.

Your response should start with 'SOLUTION:'.

PROBLEM
------------------------------
You are visiting San Francisco for the day and want to meet as many friends as possible. Solve the problem by considering various different schedules and picking the best one to optimize your goals.

Travel distances (in minutes):
Haight-Ashbury to Sunset District: 15.
Sunset District to Haight-Ashbury: 15.

CONSTRAINTS: You arrive at Haight-Ashbury at 9:00AM. Jessica will be at Sunset District from 3:15PM to 8:15PM. You'd like to meet Jessica for a minimum of 90 minutes.

Your response should start with 'SOLUTION:'.
================================================================================


ENVIRONMENT
------------------------------

(define (domain day-planning)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :negative-preconditions)
  (:types
    location time
  )
  (:predicates
    (at ?l - location)
    (at-time ?t - time)
    (next ?t1 - time ?t2 - time)
    (available-jessica ?t - time)
    (travel-15 ?from - location ?to - location)
    (meeting-with-jessica)
    (need5) (need4) (need3) (need2) (need1)
    (met-jessica-min)
  )

  (:action wait
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time ?l - location)
    :precondition (and
      (at-time ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at ?l)
      (not (meeting-with-jessica))
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at-time ?t))
      (at-time ?t2)
    )
  )

  (:action move
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time ?from - location ?to - location)
    :precondition (and
      (at-time ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at ?from)
      (travel-15 ?from ?to)
      (not (meeting-with-jessica))
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at-time ?t))
      (at-time ?t2)
      (not (at ?from))
      (at ?to)
    )
  )

  (:action start_meeting_jessica
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time ?loc - location)
    :precondition (and
      (at-time ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at ?loc)
      (available-jessica ?t)
      (available-jessica ?t2)
      (not (meeting-with-jessica))
      (not (met-jessica-min))
      (at (sunset-district))
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at-time ?t))
      (at-time ?t2)
      (meeting-with-jessica)
      (need5)
    )
  )

  (:action continue_meeting_jessica_5

      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at ?loc)
      (meeting-with-jessica)
      (need5)
      (available-jessica ?t)

    )

  (:domain day-planning)
  (:objects
    haight-ashbury sunset-district - location
    t0900 t0915 t0930 t0945
    t1000 t1015 t1030 t1045

    (available-jessica t1845)
    (available-jessica t1900)
    (available-jessica t1915)
    (available-jessica t1930)
    (available-jessica t1945)
    (available-jessica t2000)
    (available-jessica t2015)
  )
  (:goal
    (and
      (met-jessica-min)
    )
  )
)
</problem>
================================================================================


DOMAIN
------------------------------
(define (domain day-planning)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :negative-preconditions)
  (:types
    location time
  )
  (:predicates
    (at ?l - location)
    (at-time ?t - time)
    (next ?t1 - time ?t2 - time)
    (available-jessica ?t - time)
    (travel-15 ?from - location ?to - location)
    (meeting-with-jessica)
    (need5) (need4) (need3) (need2) (need1)
    (met-jessica-min)
  )

  (:action wait
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time ?l - location)
    :precondition (and
      (at-time ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at ?l)
      (not (meeting-with-jessica))
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at-time ?t))
      (at-time ?t2)
    )
  )

  (:action move
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time ?from - location ?to - location)
    :precondition (and
      (at-time ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at ?from)
      (travel-15 ?from ?to)
      (not (meeting-with-jessica))
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at-time ?t))
      (at-time ?t2)
      (not (at ?from))
      (at ?to)
    )
  )

  (:action start_meeting_jessica
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time ?loc - location)
    :precondition (and
      (at-time ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at ?loc)
      (available-jessica ?t)
      (available-jessica ?t2)
      (not (meeting-with-jessica))
      (not (met-jessica-min))
      (at (sunset-district))
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at-time ?t))
      (at-time ?t2)
      (meeting-with-jessica)
      (need5)
    )
  )

  (:action continue_meeting_jessica_5
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time ?loc - location)
    :precondition (and
      (at-time ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at ?loc)
      (meeting-with-jessica)
      (need5)
      (available-jessica ?t)
      (available-jessica ?t2)
      (at (sunset-district))
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at-time ?t))
      (at-time ?t2)
      (not (need5))
      (need4)
    )
  )

  (:action continue_meeting_jessica_4
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time ?loc - location)
    :precondition (and
      (at-time ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at ?loc)
      (meeting-with-jessica)
      (need4)
      (available-jessica ?t)
      (available-jessica ?t2)
      (at (sunset-district))
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at-time ?t))
      (at-time ?t2)
      (not (need4))
      (need3)
    )
  )

  (:action continue_meeting_jessica_3
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time ?loc - location)
    :precondition (and
      (at-time ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at ?loc)
      (meeting-with-jessica)
      (need3)
      (available-jessica ?t)
      (available-jessica ?t2)
      (at (sunset-district))
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at-time ?t))
      (at-time ?t2)
      (not (need3))
      (need2)
    )
  )

  (:action continue_meeting_jessica_2
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time ?loc - location)
    :precondition (and
      (at-time ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at ?loc)
      (meeting-with-jessica)
      (need2)
      (available-jessica ?t)
      (available-jessica ?t2)
      (at (sunset-district))
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at-time ?t))
      (at-time ?t2)
      (not (need2))
      (need1)
    )
  )

  (:action continue_meeting_jessica_1
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time ?loc - location)
    :precondition (and
      (at-time ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at ?loc)
      (meeting-with-jessica)
      (need1)
      (available-jessica ?t)
      (available-jessica ?t2)
      (at (sunset-district))
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at-time ?t))
      (at-time ?t2)
      (not (need1))
      (not (meeting-with-jessica))
      (met-jessica-min)
    )
  )
)
================================================================================


PROBLEM
------------------------------
(define (problem meet-jessica-day)
  (:domain day-planning)
  (:objects
    haight-ashbury sunset-district - location
    t0900 t0915 t0930 t0945
    t1000 t1015 t1030 t1045
    t1100 t1115 t1130 t1145
    t1200 t1215 t1230 t1245
    t1300 t1315 t1330 t1345
    t1400 t1415 t1430 t1445
    t1500 t1515 t1530 t1545
    t1600 t1615 t1630 t1645
    t1700 t1715 t1730 t1745
    t1800 t1815 t1830 t1845
    t1900 t1915 t1930 t1945
    t2000 t2015 t2030 t2045
    t2100 - time
  )
  (:init
    (at haight-ashbury)
    (at-time t0900)

    (travel-15 haight-ashbury sunset-district)
    (travel-15 sunset-district haight-ashbury)

    (next t0900 t0915)
    (next t0915 t0930)
    (next t0930 t0945)
    (next t0945 t1000)
    (next t1000 t1015)
    (next t1015 t1030)
    (next t1030 t1045)
    (next t1045 t1100)
    (next t1100 t1115)
    (next t1115 t1130)
    (next t1130 t1145)
    (next t1145 t1200)
    (next t1200 t1215)
    (next t1215 t1230)
    (next t1230 t1245)
    (next t1245 t1300)
    (next t1300 t1315)
    (next t1315 t1330)
    (next t1330 t1345)
    (next t1345 t1400)
    (next t1400 t1415)
    (next t1415 t1430)
    (next t1430 t1445)
    (next t1445 t1500)
    (next t1500 t1515)
    (next t1515 t1530)
    (next t1530 t1545)
    (next t1545 t1600)
    (next t1600 t1615)
    (next t1615 t1630)
    (next t1630 t1645)
    (next t1645 t1700)
    (next t1700 t1715)
    (next t1715 t1730)
    (next t1730 t1745)
    (next t1745 t1800)
    (next t1800 t1815)
    (next t1815 t1830)
    (next t1830 t1845)
    (next t1845 t1900)
    (next t1900 t1915)
    (next t1915 t1930)
    (next t1930 t1945)
    (next t1945 t2000)
    (next t2000 t2015)
    (next t2015 t2030)
    (next t2030 t2045)
    (next t2045 t2100)

    (available-jessica t1515)
    (available-jessica t1530)
    (available-jessica t1545)
    (available-jessica t1600)
    (available-jessica t1615)
    (available-jessica t1630)
    (available-jessica t1645)
    (available-jessica t1700)
    (available-jessica t1715)
    (available-jessica t1730)
    (available-jessica t1745)
    (available-jessica t1800)
    (available-jessica t1815)
    (available-jessica t1830)
    (available-jessica t1845)
    (available-jessica t1900)
    (available-jessica t1915)
    (available-jessica t1930)
    (available-jessica t1945)
    (available-jessica t2000)
    (available-jessica t2015)
  )
  (:goal
    (and
      (met-jessica-min)
    )
  )
)

PROBLEM
------------------------------
You are visiting San Francisco for the day and want to meet as many friends as possible. Solve the problem by considering various different schedules and picking the best one to optimize your goals.

Travel distances (in minutes):
Bayview to Golden Gate Park: 22.
Golden Gate Park to Bayview: 23.

CONSTRAINTS: You arrive at Bayview at 9:00AM. Barbara will be at Golden Gate Park from 8:00AM to 11:30AM. You'd like to meet Barbara for a minimum of 90 minutes.

Your response should start with 'SOLUTION:'.
================================================================================


ENVIRONMENT
------------------------------
You are visiting San Francisco for the day and want to meet as many friends as possible. Solve the problem by considering various different schedules and picking the best one to optimize your goals.

Travel distances (in minutes):
Bayview to Golden Gate Park: 22.
Golden Gate Park to Bayview: 23.

CONSTRAINTS: You arrive at Bayview at 9:00AM. Barbara will be at Golden Gate Park from 8:00AM to 11:30AM. You'd like to meet Barbara for a minimum of 90 minutes.

Your response should start with 'SOLUTION:'.
================================================================================


FINAL-PLAN
------------------------------
<domain>
(define (domain meeting-planner-sf)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :negative-preconditions :numeric-fluents)
  (:types
    location person
  )
  (:predicates
    (at ?l - location)
    (person_at ?p - person ?l - location)
  )
  (:functions
    (time)
    (travel_time ?from ?to - location)
    (remaining_need ?p - person)
    (avail_start ?p - person)
    (avail_end ?p - person)
  )

  (:action travel
    :parameters (?from - location ?to - location)
    :precondition (at ?from)
    :effect (and
      (not (at ?from))
      (at ?to)
      (increase (time) (travel_time ?from ?to))
    )
  )

  (:action meet-10
    :parameters (?p - person ?l - location)
    :precondition (and
      (at ?l)
      (person_at ?p ?l)
      (>= (time) (avail_start ?p))
      (<= (time) (- (avail_end ?p) 10))
      (>= (remaining_need ?p) 10)
    )
    :effect (and
      (increase (time) 10)
      (decrease (remaining_need ?p) 10)
    )
  )
)
</domain>
<problem>
(define (problem meeting-planner-sf-prob)
  (:domain meeting-planner-sf)
  (:objects
    bayview ggp - location
    barbara - person
  )
  (:init
    (at bayview)
    (person_at barbara ggp)
    (= (time) 540)
    (= (travel_time bayview ggp) 22)
    (= (travel_time ggp bayview) 23)
    (= (avail_start barbara) 480)
    (= (avail_end barbara) 690)
    (= (remaining_need barbara) 90)
  )
  (:goal
    (<= (remaining_need barbara) 0)
  )
  (:metric minimize (time))
)
</problem>
================================================================================


DOMAIN
------------------------------
(define (domain meeting-planner-sf)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :negative-preconditions :numeric-fluents)
  (:types
    location person
  )
  (:predicates
    (at ?l - location)
    (person_at ?p - person ?l - location)
  )
  (:functions
    (time)
    (travel_time ?from ?to - location)
    (remaining_need ?p - person)
    (avail_start ?p - person)
    (avail_end ?p - person)
  )

  (:action travel
    :parameters (?from - location ?to - location)
    :precondition (at ?from)
    :effect (and
      (not (at ?from))
      (at ?to)
      (increase (time) (travel_time ?from ?to))
    )
  )

  (:action meet-10
    :parameters (?p - person ?l - location)
    :precondition (and
      (at ?l)
      (person_at ?p ?l)
      (>= (time) (avail_start ?p))
      (<= (time) (- (avail_end ?p) 10))
      (>= (remaining_need ?p) 10)
    )
    :effect (and
      (increase (time) 10)
      (decrease (remaining_need ?p) 10)
    )
  )
)
================================================================================


PROBLEM
------------------------------
(define (problem meeting-planner-sf-prob)
  (:domain meeting-planner-sf)
  (:objects
    bayview ggp - location
    barbara - person
  )
  (:init
    (at bayview)
    (person_at barbara ggp)
    (= (time) 540)
    (= (travel_time bayview ggp) 22)
    (= (travel_time ggp bayview) 23)
    (= (avail_start barbara) 480)
    (= (avail_end barbara) 690)
    (= (remaining_need barbara) 90)
  )
  (:goal
    (<= (remaining_need barbara) 0)
  )
  (:metric minimize (time))
)

Feasible but finishes later with no added benefit.\n\n- Schedule C: Longer catch-up with Barbara (preference), exceeding minimum.\n  1) Travel Bayview -> Golden Gate Park: 540\u2013562 (09:00\u201309:22).\n  2) Meet Barbara 100 minutes: 562\u2013662 (09:22\u201311:02) in 10\u00d710-min blocks.\n  End time: 662 (11:02). Feasible and honors a soft preference, but not better for \u201cmeet as many friends\u201d given only Barbara is known.\n\nSelected best schedule: Schedule A (earliest completion while meeting Barbara\u2019s minimum within her availability)."
}

PROBLEM
------------------------------
You are visiting San Francisco for the day and want to meet as many friends as possible. Solve the problem by considering various different schedules and picking the best one to optimize your goals.

Travel distances (in minutes):
Presidio to Marina District: 10.
Marina District to Presidio: 10.

CONSTRAINTS: You arrive at Presidio at 9:00AM. Jessica will be at Marina District from 9:15AM to 5:45PM. You'd like to meet Jessica for a minimum of 60 minutes.

ENVIRONMENT
------------------------------
You are visiting San Francisco for the day and want to meet as many friends as possible. Solve the problem by considering various different schedules and picking the best one to optimize your goals.

Travel distances (in minutes):
Presidio to Marina District: 10.
Marina District to Presidio: 10.

CONSTRAINTS: You arrive at Presidio at 9:00AM. Jessica will be at Marina District from 9:15AM to 5:45PM. You'd like to meet Jessica for a minimum of 60 minutes.

<domain>
(define (domain sf-5min-scheduling)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :negative-preconditions)
  (:types
    time loc
  )
  (:predicates
    ; time progression
    (now ?t - time)
    (next ?t1 - time ?t2 - time)

    ; locations and movement (San Francisco: Presidio <-> Marina District)
    (at ?l - loc)
    (intransit-pm) ; in transit from Presidio to Marina (first 5-min leg completed)
    (intransit-mp) ; in transit from Marina to Presidio (first 5-min leg completed)

    ; static availability for meeting Jessica (enabled timepoints for starting/continuing a 5-min meeting step)
    (avail-jessica ?t - time)

    ; static allowed departure times for Presidio -> Marina
    (depart-pm-allowed ?t - time)

    ; meeting streak tracking (consecutive 5-min meeting steps at Marina)
    (streak1)
    (streak2)
    (streak3)
    (streak4)
    (streak5)
    (streak6)
    (streak7)
    (streak8)
    (streak9)
    (streak10)
    (streak11)
    (streak12)

    ; achieved at least 12 consecutive steps (>= 60 minutes) meeting with Jessica
    (achieved12)
  )

  ; wait one 5-minute step at Presidio
  (:action wait-at-presidio
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at presidio)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
  )

  ; wait one 5-minute step at Marina
  (:action wait-at-marina
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at marina)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
  )

  ; travel Presidio -> Marina, first leg (5 minutes)
  (:action travel-pm-step1
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at presidio)
      (depart-pm-allowed ?t)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (at presidio))
      (intransit-pm)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
  )

  ; travel Presidio -> Marina, second leg (5 minutes), arrival at Marina
  (:action travel-pm-step2
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (intransit-pm)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (intransit-pm))
      (at marina)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
  )

  ; travel Marina -> Presidio, first leg (5 minutes)
  (:action travel-mp-step1
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at marina)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (at marina))
      (intransit-mp)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
  )

  ; travel Marina -> Presidio, second leg (5 minutes), arrival at Presidio
  (:action travel-mp-step2
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (intransit-mp)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (intransit-mp))
      (at presidio)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
  )

  ; meeting steps at Marina, enabled only during Jessica's availability at current timepoint

  ; start a meeting streak (first 5-minute meeting slice)
  (:action meet-from-0
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at marina)
      (avail-jessica ?t)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (streak1)
    )
  )

  (:action meet-1-to-2
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak1))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak1)) (streak2))
  )

  (:action meet-2-to-3
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak2))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak2)) (streak3))
  )

  (:action meet-3-to-4
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak3))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak3)) (streak4))
  )

  (:action meet-4-to-5
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak4))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak4)) (streak5))
  )

  (:action meet-5-to-6
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak5))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak5)) (streak6))
  )

  (:action meet-6-to-7
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)

  )

  (:action meet-7-to-8
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak7))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak7)) (streak8))
  )

  (:action meet-8-to-9
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak8))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak8)) (streak9))
  )

  (:action meet-9-to-10
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak9))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak9)) (streak10))

  (:action meet-10-to-11

  (:action meet-11-to-12

      (now ?t2)
      (not (streak11))
      (streak12)

<problem>

  (:domain sf-5min-scheduling)
  (:objects
    ; locations
    presidio marina - loc

    ; timepoints from 09:00 to 17:45 in 5-minute steps

    (depart-pm-allowed t1215)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1220)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1225)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1230)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1235)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1240)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1245)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1250)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1255)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1300)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1305)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1310)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1315)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1320)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1325)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1330)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1335)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1340)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1345)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1350)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1355)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1400)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1405)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1410)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1415)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1420)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1425)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1430)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1435)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1440)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1445)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1450)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1455)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1500)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1505)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1510)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1515)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1520)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1525)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1530)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1535)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1540)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1545)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1550)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1555)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1600)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1605)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1610)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1615)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1620)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1625)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1630)
    (depart-pm-allowed t1635)
  )
  (:goal
    (and
      (achieved12)
    )
  )
)
</problem>
================================================================================


DOMAIN
------------------------------
(define (domain sf-5min-scheduling)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :negative-preconditions)
  (:types
    time loc
  )
  (:predicates
    ; time progression
    (now ?t - time)
    (next ?t1 - time ?t2 - time)

    ; locations and movement (San Francisco: Presidio <-> Marina District)
    (at ?l - loc)
    (intransit-pm) ; in transit from Presidio to Marina (first 5-min leg completed)
    (intransit-mp) ; in transit from Marina to Presidio (first 5-min leg completed)

    ; static availability for meeting Jessica (enabled timepoints for starting/continuing a 5-min meeting step)
    (avail-jessica ?t - time)

    ; static allowed departure times for Presidio -> Marina
    (depart-pm-allowed ?t - time)

    ; meeting streak tracking (consecutive 5-min meeting steps at Marina)
    (streak1)
    (streak2)
    (streak3)
    (streak4)
    (streak5)
    (streak6)
    (streak7)
    (streak8)
    (streak9)
    (streak10)
    (streak11)
    (streak12)

    ; achieved at least 12 consecutive steps (>= 60 minutes) meeting with Jessica
    (achieved12)
  )

  ; wait one 5-minute step at Presidio
  (:action wait-at-presidio
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at presidio)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
  )

  ; wait one 5-minute step at Marina
  (:action wait-at-marina
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at marina)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
  )

  ; travel Presidio -> Marina, first leg (5 minutes)
  (:action travel-pm-step1
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at presidio)
      (depart-pm-allowed ?t)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (at presidio))
      (intransit-pm)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
  )

  ; travel Presidio -> Marina, second leg (5 minutes), arrival at Marina
  (:action travel-pm-step2
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (intransit-pm)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (intransit-pm))
      (at marina)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
  )

  ; travel Marina -> Presidio, first leg (5 minutes)
  (:action travel-mp-step1
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at marina)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (at marina))
      (intransit-mp)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
  )

  ; travel Marina -> Presidio, second leg (5 minutes), arrival at Presidio
  (:action travel-mp-step2
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (intransit-mp)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (intransit-mp))
      (at presidio)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
  )

  ; meeting steps at Marina, enabled only during Jessica's availability at current timepoint

  ; start a meeting streak (first 5-minute meeting slice)
  (:action meet-from-0
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t)
      (next ?t ?t2)
      (at marina)
      (avail-jessica ?t)
      (not (streak1))
      (not (streak2))
      (not (streak3))
      (not (streak4))
      (not (streak5))
      (not (streak6))
      (not (streak7))
      (not (streak8))
      (not (streak9))
      (not (streak10))
      (not (streak11))
      (not (streak12))
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (streak1)
    )
  )

  (:action meet-1-to-2
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak1))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak1)) (streak2))
  )

  (:action meet-2-to-3
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak2))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak2)) (streak3))
  )

  (:action meet-3-to-4
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak3))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak3)) (streak4))
  )

  (:action meet-4-to-5
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak4))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak4)) (streak5))
  )

  (:action meet-5-to-6
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak5))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak5)) (streak6))
  )

  (:action meet-6-to-7
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak6))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak6)) (streak7))
  )

  (:action meet-7-to-8
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak7))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak7)) (streak8))
  )

  (:action meet-8-to-9
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak8))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak8)) (streak9))
  )

  (:action meet-9-to-10
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak9))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak9)) (streak10))
  )

  (:action meet-10-to-11
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak10))
    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (streak10)) (streak11))
  )

  (:action meet-11-to-12
    :parameters (?t - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (at marina) (avail-jessica ?t) (streak11))
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (streak11))
      (streak12)
      (achieved12)
    )
  )
)
================================================================================


PROBLEM
------------------------------
(define (problem sf-5min-scheduling-problem)
  (:domain sf-5min-scheduling)
  (:objects
    ; locations
    presidio marina - loc

    ; timepoints from 09:00 to 17:45 in 5-minute steps
    t0900 t0905 t0910 t0915 t0920 t0925 t0930 t0935 t0940 t0945 t0950 t0955
    t1000 t1005 t1010 t1015 t1020 t1025 t1030 t1035 t1040 t1045 t1050 t1055
    t1100 t1105 t1110 t1115 t1120 t1125 t1130 t1135 t1140 t1145 t1150 t1155
    t1200 t1205 t1210 t1215 t1220 t1225 t1230 t1235 t1240 t1245 t1250 t1255
    t1300 t1305 t1310 t1315 t1320 t1325 t1330 t1335 t1340 t1345 t1350 t1355
    t1400 t1405 t1410 t1415 t1420 t1425 t1430 t1435 t1440 t1445 t1450 t1455
    t1500 t1505 t1510 t1515 t1520 t1525 t1530 t1535 t1540 t1545 t1550 t1555
    t1600 t1605 t1610 t1615 t1620 t1625 t1630 t1635 t1640 t1645 t1650 t1655
    t1700 t1705 t1710 t1715 t1720 t1725 t1730 t1735 t1740 t1745 - time
  )
  (:init
    ; starting state
    (at presidio)
    (now t0900)

    ; successor relation between all adjacent 5-minute timepoints
    (next t0900 t0905)
    (next t0905 t0910)
    (next t0910 t0915)
    (next t0915 t0920)
    (next t0920 t0925)
    (next t0925 t0930)
    (next t0930 t0935)
    (next t0935 t0940)
    (next t0940 t0945)

    (next t1320 t1325)
    (next t1325 t1330)

(define (domain meet-william)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :action-costs)
  (:types agent location time)
  (:predicates
    (at ?a - agent ?l - location)
    (current-time ?t - time)
    (next ?t1 - time ?t2 - time)
    (william-available ?t - time)
    (met-william)
  )
  (:functions (total-cost))

  (:action wait-1
    :parameters (?a - agent ?t0 - time ?t1 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (current-time ?t0)
      (next ?t0 ?t1)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (current-time ?t0))
      (current-time ?t1)
      (increase (total-cost) 1)
    )

================================================================================


DOMAIN
------------------------------
(define (domain meet-william)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :action-costs)
  (:types agent location time)
  (:predicates
    (at ?a - agent ?l - location)
    (current-time ?t - time)
    (next ?t1 - time ?t2 - time)
    (william-available ?t - time)
    (met-william)
  )
  (:functions (total-cost))

  (:action wait-1
    :parameters (?a - agent ?t0 - time ?t1 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (current-time ?t0)
      (next ?t0 ?t1)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (current-time ?t0))
      (current-time ?t1)
      (increase (total-cost) 1)
    )
  )

  (:action move-nob_hill-to-the_castro
    :parameters (?a - agent
                 ?t0 - time ?t1 - time ?t2 - time ?t3 - time ?t4 - time ?t5 - time ?t6 - time ?t7 - time ?t8 - time ?t9 - time
                 ?t10 - time ?t11 - time ?t12 - time ?t13 - time ?t14 - time ?t15 - time ?t16 - time ?t17 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (at ?a nob_hill)
      (current-time ?t0)
      (next ?t0 ?t1)
      (next ?t1 ?t2)
      (next ?t2 ?t3)
      (next ?t3 ?t4)
      (next ?t4 ?t5)
      (next ?t5 ?t6)
      (next ?t6 ?t7)
      (next ?t7 ?t8)
      (next ?t8 ?t9)
      (next ?t9 ?t10)
      (next ?t10 ?t11)
      (next ?t11 ?t12)
      (next ?t12 ?t13)
      (next ?t13 ?t14)
      (next ?t14 ?t15)
      (next ?t15 ?t16)
      (next ?t16 ?t17)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at ?a nob_hill))
      (at ?a the_castro)
      (not (current-time ?t0))
      (current-time ?t17)
      (increase (total-cost) 17)
    )
  )

  (:action move-the_castro-to-nob_hill
    :parameters (?a - agent
                 ?u0 - time ?u1 - time ?u2 - time ?u3 - time ?u4 - time ?u5 - time ?u6 - time ?u7 - time ?u8 - time ?u9 - time
                 ?u10 - time ?u11 - time ?u12 - time ?u13 - time ?u14 - time ?u15 - time ?u16 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (at ?a the_castro)
      (current-time ?u0)
      (next ?u0 ?u1)
      (next ?u1 ?u2)
      (next ?u2 ?u3)
      (next ?u3 ?u4)
      (next ?u4 ?u5)
      (next ?u5 ?u6)
      (next ?u6 ?u7)
      (next ?u7 ?u8)
      (next ?u8 ?u9)
      (next ?u9 ?u10)
      (next ?u10 ?u11)
      (next ?u11 ?u12)
      (next ?u12 ?u13)
      (next ?u13 ?u14)
      (next ?u14 ?u15)
      (next ?u15 ?u16)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at ?a the_castro))
      (at ?a nob_hill)
      (not (current-time ?u0))
      (current-time ?u16)
      (increase (total-cost) 16)
    )
  )

  (:action meet-william-75
    :parameters (?a - agent
                 ?s0 - time ?s1 - time ?s2 - time ?s3 - time ?s4 - time ?s5 - time ?s6 - time ?s7 - time ?s8 - time ?s9 - time
                 ?s10 - time ?s11 - time ?s12 - time ?s13 - time ?s14 - time ?s15 - time ?s16 - time ?s17 - time ?s18 - time ?s19 - time
                 ?s20 - time ?s21 - time ?s22 - time ?s23 - time ?s24 - time ?s25 - time ?s26 - time ?s27 - time ?s28 - time ?s29 - time
                 ?s30 - time ?s31 - time ?s32 - time ?s33 - time ?s34 - time ?s35 - time ?s36 - time ?s37 - time ?s38 - time ?s39 - time
                 ?s40 - time ?s41 - time ?s42 - time ?s43 - time ?s44 - time ?s45 - time ?s46 - time ?s47 - time ?s48 - time ?s49 - time
                 ?s50 - time ?s51 - time ?s52 - time ?s53 - time ?s54 - time ?s55 - time ?s56 - time ?s57 - time ?s58 - time ?s59 - time
                 ?s60 - time ?s61 - time ?s62 - time ?s63 - time ?s64 - time ?s65 - time ?s66 - time ?s67 - time ?s68 - time ?s69 - time
                 ?s70 - time ?s71 - time ?s72 - time ?s73 - time ?s74 - time ?s75 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (at ?a the_castro)
      (current-time ?s0)
      (next ?s0 ?s1)
      (next ?s1 ?s2)
      (next ?s2 ?s3)
      (next ?s3 ?s4)
      (next ?s4 ?s5)
      (next ?s5 ?s6)
      (next ?s6 ?s7)
      (next ?s7 ?s8)
      (next ?s8 ?s9)
      (next ?s9 ?s10)

      (next ?s13 ?s14)
      (next ?s14 ?s15)
      (next ?s15 ?s16)
      (next ?s16 ?s17)
      (next ?s17 ?s18)

PROBLEM
------------------------------
You are visiting San Francisco for the day and want to meet as many friends as possible. Solve the problem by considering various different schedules and picking the best one to optimize your goals.

Travel distances (in minutes):
Fisherman's Wharf to Nob Hill: 11.
Nob Hill to Fisherman's Wharf: 11.

CONSTRAINTS: You arrive at Fisherman's Wharf at 9:00AM. Kenneth will be at Nob Hill from 2:15PM to 7:45PM. You'd like to meet Kenneth for a minimum of 90 minutes.

Your response should start with 'SOLUTION:'.
================================================================================


ENVIRONMENT
------------------------------
You are visiting San Francisco for the day and want to meet as many friends as possible. Solve the problem by considering various different schedules and picking the best one to optimize your goals.

Travel distances (in minutes):
Fisherman's Wharf to Nob Hill: 11.
Nob Hill to Fisherman's Wharf: 11.

CONSTRAINTS: You arrive at Fisherman's Wharf at 9:00AM. Kenneth will be at Nob Hill from 2:15PM to 7:45PM. You'd like to meet Kenneth for a minimum of 90 minutes.

Your response should start with 'SOLUTION:'.

FINAL-PLAN
------------------------------
Selected schedule: S2_max_time_with_kenneth (maximizes friends met; tie-broken by least idle time by using full 14:1519:45 meeting window). The PDDL below uses 5-minute discrete time steps. Travel between Fisherman's Wharf and Nob Hill takes 11 minutes and is conservatively rounded up to 15 minutes (encoded by requiring three successive 5-minute steps). Waiting is explicit. Meeting progresses in 5-minute quanta; the goal requires reaching 18 quanta (90 minutes).

<domain>
(define (domain sf_meet_5min)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :negative-preconditions)
  (:types
    time
    location
    mlevel
  )

  (:predicates
    ; time and movement
    (now ?t - time)                           ; current timepoint
    (next ?t1 - time ?t2 - time)              ; discrete 5-minute successor

    ; positioning
    (at ?l - location)                        ; agent at location

    ; meeting window control
    (meet-start-allowed ?t - time)            ; starting a 5-min meet step at ?t is within Kenneth's availability (ensures end <= 19:45)

    ; meeting progress counter (18 steps = 90 minutes)
    (meeting-level ?m - mlevel)               ; current accumulated 5-min meeting level
    (next-level ?m1 - mlevel ?m2 - mlevel)    ; successor meeting level
  )

  ; Waiting action: advances time by one 5-minute step
  (:action wait-5
    :parameters (?t1 - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t1)
      (next ?t1 ?t2)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t1))
      (now ?t2)
    )
  )

  ; Travel FW -> NH: 11 minutes rounded up to 15 minutes = 3 successive 5-min steps
  (:action travel-fw-to-nh
    :parameters (?t0 - time ?t1 - time ?t2 - time ?t3 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (at fishermans_wharf)
      (now ?t0)
      (next ?t0 ?t1)
      (next ?t1 ?t2)
      (next ?t2 ?t3)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at fishermans_wharf))
      (at nob_hill)
      (not (now ?t0))
      (now ?t3)
    )
  )

  ; Travel NH -> FW: 11 minutes rounded up to 15 minutes = 3 successive 5-min steps
  (:action travel-nh-to-fw
    :parameters (?t0 - time ?t1 - time ?t2 - time ?t3 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (at nob_hill)
      (now ?t0)
      (next ?t0 ?t1)
      (next ?t1 ?t2)
      (next ?t2 ?t3)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at nob_hill))
      (at fishermans_wharf)
      (not (now ?t0))
      (now ?t3)
    )
  )

  ; Meet Kenneth for one 5-minute quantum; only allowed entirely within 14:1519:45
  ; Repeating this action 18 times (consecutively or with waits between) achieves the 90-minute minimum requirement.
  (:action meet-kenneth-5
    :parameters (?t1 - time ?t2 - time ?m1 - mlevel ?m2 - mlevel)
    :precondition (and
      (at nob_hill)
      (now ?t1)
      (next ?t1 ?t2)
      (meet-start-allowed ?t1)
      (meeting-level ?m1)
      (next-level ?m1 ?m2)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t1))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (meeting-level ?m1))
      (meeting-level ?m2)
    )
  )
)
</domain>

    (meet-start-allowed t1935)
    (meet-start-allowed t1940)

  ; Goal: meet Kenneth for at least 90 minutes (18 x 5-minute steps)
  (:goal (meeting-level l18))
)
</problem>
================================================================================


DOMAIN
------------------------------
(define (domain sf_meet_5min)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :negative-preconditions)
  (:types
    time
    location
    mlevel
  )

  (:predicates
    ; time and movement
    (now ?t - time)                           ; current timepoint
    (next ?t1 - time ?t2 - time)              ; discrete 5-minute successor

    ; positioning
    (at ?l - location)                        ; agent at location

    ; meeting window control
    (meet-start-allowed ?t - time)            ; starting a 5-min meet step at ?t is within Kenneth's availability (ensures end <= 19:45)

    ; meeting progress counter (18 steps = 90 minutes)
    (meeting-level ?m - mlevel)               ; current accumulated 5-min meeting level
    (next-level ?m1 - mlevel ?m2 - mlevel)    ; successor meeting level
  )

  ; Waiting action: advances time by one 5-minute step
  (:action wait-5
    :parameters (?t1 - time ?t2 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (now ?t1)
      (next ?t1 ?t2)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t1))
      (now ?t2)
    )
  )

  ; Travel FW -> NH: 11 minutes rounded up to 15 minutes = 3 successive 5-min steps
  (:action travel-fw-to-nh
    :parameters (?t0 - time ?t1 - time ?t2 - time ?t3 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (at fishermans_wharf)
      (now ?t0)
      (next ?t0 ?t1)
      (next ?t1 ?t2)
      (next ?t2 ?t3)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at fishermans_wharf))
      (at nob_hill)
      (not (now ?t0))
      (now ?t3)
    )
  )

  ; Travel NH -> FW: 11 minutes rounded up to 15 minutes = 3 successive 5-min steps
  (:action travel-nh-to-fw
    :parameters (?t0 - time ?t1 - time ?t2 - time ?t3 - time)
    :precondition (and
      (at nob_hill)
      (now ?t0)
      (next ?t0 ?t1)
      (next ?t1 ?t2)
      (next ?t2 ?t3)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (at nob_hill))
      (at fishermans_wharf)
      (not (now ?t0))
      (now ?t3)
    )
  )

  ; Meet Kenneth for one 5-minute quantum; only allowed entirely within 14:1519:45
  ; Repeating this action 18 times (consecutively or with waits between) achieves the 90-minute minimum requirement.
  (:action meet-kenneth-5
    :parameters (?t1 - time ?t2 - time ?m1 - mlevel ?m2 - mlevel)
    :precondition (and
      (at nob_hill)
      (now ?t1)
      (next ?t1 ?t2)
      (meet-start-allowed ?t1)
      (meeting-level ?m1)
      (next-level ?m1 ?m2)
    )
    :effect (and
      (not (now ?t1))
      (now ?t2)
      (not (meeting-level ?m1))
      (meeting-level ?m2)
    )
  )
)
================================================================================


PROBLEM
------------------------------
(define (problem sf_meet_5min_instance)
  (:domain sf_meet_5min)

  (:objects
    ; locations
    fishermans_wharf nob_hill - location

    ; meeting progress levels: l0..l18 (18 steps = 90 minutes)
    l0 l1 l2 l3 l4 l5 l6 l7 l8 l9 l10 l11 l12 l13 l14 l15 l16 l17 l18 - mlevel

    ; timepoints (5-minute grid) from 09:00 to 21:00 inclusive
    t0900 t0905 t0910 t0915 t0920 t0925 t0930 t0935 t0940 t0945 t0950 t0955
    t1000 t1005 t1010 t1015 t1020 t1025 t1030 t1035 t1040 t1045 t1050 t1055
    t1100 t1105 t1110 t1115 t1120 t1125 t1130 t1135 t1140 t1145 t1150 t1155
    t1200 t1205 t1210 t1215 t1220 t1225 t1230 t1235 t1240 t1245 t1250 t1255
    t1300 t1305 t1310 t1315 t1320 t1325 t1330 t1335 t1340 t1345 t1350 t1355
    t1400 t1405 t1410 t1415 t1420 t1425 t1430 t1435 t1440 t1445 t1450 t1455
    t1500 t1505 t1510 t1515 t1520 t1525 t1530 t1535 t1540 t1545 t1550 t1555
    t1600 t1605 t1610 t1615 t1620 t1625 t1630 t1635 t1640 t1645 t1650 t1655

    t1800 t1805 t1810 t1815 t1820 t1825 t1830 t1835 t1840 t1845 t1850 t1855
    t1900 t1905 t1910 t1915 t1920 t1925 t1930 t1935 t1940 t1945 t1950 t1955

    t2100 - time

    "pddl_domain": "(define (domain meeting-planning-example8)\n  (:requirements :strips :typing :negative-preconditions :action-costs)\n  (:types location minute count)\n  (:predicates\n    (at ?l - location)\n    (now ?t - minute)\n    (next ?t1 - minute ?t2 - minute)\n    (steph-available ?t - minute)\n    (traveling-c2m)\n    (traveling-m2c)\n    (elapsed-c2m ?c - count)\n    (elapsed-m2c ?c - count)\n    (next-count ?c1 - count ?c2 - count)\n    (met-count ?c - count)\n    (in-meeting)\n  )\n  (:functions (total-cost))\n\n  ; Start travel from Chinatown to Marina (12 minutes total)\n  (:action start-travel-c2m\n    :precondition (and (at chinatown) (not (traveling-c2m)) (not (traveling-m2c)))\n    :effect (and (not (at chinatown)) (traveling-c2m) (elapsed-c2m c0))\n  )\n\n  (:action travel-advance-c2m\n    :parameters (?t - minute ?t2 - minute ?c - count ?c2 - count)\n    :precondition (and (traveling-c2m) (elapsed-c2m ?c) (next-count ?c ?c2) (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2))\n    :effect (and (not (elapsed-c2m ?c)) (elapsed-c2m ?c2) (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (increase (total-cost) 1))\n  )\n\n  (:action complete-travel-c2m\n    :precondition (and (traveling-c2m) (elapsed-c2m c12))\n    :effect (and (not (traveling-c2m)) (not (elapsed-c2m c12)) (at marina_district))\n  )\n\n  ; Start travel from Marina to Chinatown (16 minutes total)\n  (:action start-travel-m2c\n    :precondition (and (at marina_district) (not (traveling-c2m)) (not (traveling-m2c)))\n    :effect (and (not (at marina_district)) (traveling-m2c) (elapsed-m2c c0))\n  )\n\n  (:action travel-advance-m2c\n    :parameters (?t - minute ?t2 - minute ?c - count ?c2 - count)\n    :precondition (and (traveling-m2c) (elapsed-m2c ?c) (next-count ?c ?c2) (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2))\n    :effect (and (not (elapsed-m2c ?c)) (elapsed-m2c ?c2) (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (increase (total-cost) 1))\n  )\n\n  (:action complete-travel-m2c\n    :precondition (and (traveling-m2c) (elapsed-m2c c16))\n    :effect (and (not (traveling-m2c)) (not (elapsed-m2c c16)) (at chinatown))\n  )\n\n  ; Idle wait advancing time by one minute (only when not in transit or in a meeting)\n  (:action wait\n    :parameters (?t - minute ?t2 - minute)\n    :precondition (and (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (not (traveling-c2m)) (not (traveling-m2c)) (not (in-meeting)))\n    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (increase (total-cost) 1))\n  )\n\n  ; Begin meeting with Stephanie (only once, before accumulating minutes)\n  (:action begin-meeting\n    :parameters (?t - minute)\n    :precondition (and (at marina_district) (now ?t) (steph-available ?t) (met-count c0) (not (in-meeting)) (not (traveling-c2m)) (not (traveling-m2c)))\n    :effect (in-meeting)\n  )\n\n  ; Accumulate one minute of meeting with Stephanie (must be within availability)\n  (:action meet-step\n    :parameters (?t - minute ?t2 - minute ?c - count ?c2 - count)\n    :precondition (and (in-meeting) (at marina_district) (now ?t) (next ?t ?t2) (steph-available ?t) (met-count ?c) (next-count ?c ?c2))\n    :effect (and (not (now ?t)) (now ?t2) (not (met-count ?c)) (met-count ?c2) (increase (total-cost) 1))\n  )\n\n  ; Optionally end the meeting after reaching the required minutes\n  (:action end-meeting\n    :precondition (and (in-meeting) (met-count c105))\n    :effect (not (in-meeting))\n  )\n)",

PROBLEM
------------------------------
You are visiting San Francisco for the day and want to meet as many friends as possible. Solve the problem by considering various different schedules and picking the best one to optimize your goals.

Travel distances (in minutes):
Union Square to Nob Hill: 9.
Nob Hill to Union Square: 7.

================================================================================


ENVIRONMENT
------------------------------
You are visiting San Francisco for the day and want to meet as many friends as possible. Solve the problem by considering various different schedules and picking the best one to optimize your goals.

Travel distances (in minutes):
Union Square to Nob Hill: 9.
Nob Hill to Union Square: 7.

CONSTRAINTS: You arrive at Union Square at 9:00AM. Mary will be at Nob Hill from 12:00PM to 4:15PM. You'd like to meet Mary for a minimum of 75 minutes.

Your response should start with 'SOLUTION:'.
================================================================================


FINAL-PLAN
------------------------------
<domain>
(define (domain meet-mary)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :negative-preconditions :fluents :numeric-fluents :action-costs)
  (:types location person)
  (:predicates
    (at ?l - location)
    (met ?p - person)
    (friend-location ?p - person ?l - location)
  )
  (:functions
    (current-time)
    (total-cost)
    (travel-time ?from ?to - location)
    (avail-start ?p - person)
    (avail-end ?p - person)
    (latest-start ?p - person)
  )

  (:action travel
    :parameters (?from ?to - location)
    :precondition (at ?from)
    :effect (and
      (not (at ?from))
      (at ?to)
      (increase (current-time) (travel-time ?from ?to))
      (increase (total-cost) (travel-time ?from ?to))
    )
  )

  (:action wait-until-noon
    :parameters ()
    :precondition (&lt; (current-time) 720)
    :effect (assign (current-time) 720)
  )

  (:action meet-friend-75
    :parameters (?p - person ?l - location)
    :precondition (and
      (friend-location ?p ?l)
      (at ?l)
      (not (met ?p))
      (>= (current-time) (avail-start ?p))
      (<= (current-time) (latest-start ?p))
      (<= (+ (current-time) 75) (avail-end ?p))
    )
    :effect (and
      (met ?p)
      (increase (current-time) 75)
    )
  )
)
</domain>
<problem>
(define (problem meet-mary-problem)
  (:domain meet-mary)
  (:objects
    union_square nob_hill - location
    mary - person
  )
  (:init
    (at union_square)
    (friend-location mary nob_hill)
    (= (current-time) 540)
    (= (total-cost) 0)
    (= (travel-time union_square nob_hill) 9)
    (= (travel-time nob_hill union_square) 7)
    (= (avail-start mary) 720)
    (= (latest-start mary) 900)
    (= (avail-end mary) 975)
  )
  (:goal (met mary))
  (:metric minimize (total-cost))
)
</problem>
================================================================================


DOMAIN
------------------------------
(define (domain meet-mary)
  (:requirements :strips :typing :negative-preconditions :fluents :numeric-fluents :action-costs)
  (:types location person)
  (:predicates
    (at ?l - location)
    (met ?p - person)
    (friend-location ?p - person ?l - location)
  )
  (:functions
    (current-time)
    (total-cost)
    (travel-time ?from ?to - location)
    (avail-start ?p - person)
    (avail-end ?p - person)
    (latest-start ?p - person)
  )

  (:action travel
    :parameters (?from ?to - location)
    :precondition (at ?from)
    :effect (and
      (not (at ?from))
      (at ?to)
      (increase (current-time) (travel-time ?from ?to))
      (increase (total-cost) (travel-time ?from ?to))
    )
  )

  (:action wait-until-noon
    :parameters ()
    :precondition (&lt; (current-time) 720)
    :effect (assign (current-time) 720)
  )

  (:action meet-friend-75
    :parameters (?p - person ?l - location)
    :precondition (and
      (friend-location ?p ?l)
      (at ?l)
      (not (met ?p))
      (>= (current-time) (avail-start ?p))
      (<= (current-time) (latest-start ?p))
      (<= (+ (current-time) 75) (avail-end ?p))
    )
    :effect (and
      (met ?p)
      (increase (current-time) 75)
    )
  )
)
================================================================================


PROBLEM
------------------------------
(define (problem meet-mary-problem)
  (:domain meet-mary)
  (:objects
    union_square nob_hill - location
    mary - person
  )
  (:init
    (at union_square)
    (friend-location mary nob_hill)
    (= (current-time) 540)
    (= (total-cost) 0)
    (= (travel-time union_square nob_hill) 9)
    (= (travel-time nob_hill union_square) 7)
    (= (avail-start mary) 720)
    (= (latest-start mary) 900)
    (= (avail-end mary) 975)
  )
  (:goal (met mary))
  (:metric minimize (total-cost))
)
================================================================================
